gricultural Library, Maryland, USA in the year 2007 and Commonwealth Professional Fellowship, UK at Middlesex University, London, UK in the year 2011.'),(312,'Dean Academic Affairs','See content','Not Available','dean.academic@bbau.ac.in','https://www.bbau.ac.in/DeanAcademic.aspx','Dean Academic affairs\nAlumni Cell\nChief Vigilance Officer\nDeans of School\nHeads of Department\nOther / Important Centre\'s\nAcademics\nAcademics\nDean Academic Affairs\nM.Phil / Ph.D Regulations\nMOU\nConsultancy\nCourse folder\nAcademic Calender\nHolidays\nInstitutional Academic Integrity Panel (IAIP)\nCentre for Industry Institution Partnership Program (CIIPP)\nIQAC\nAbout\nIQAC\nAcademic Flexibility\nFoundation Course\nChoice Based Credit System\nPublications\nAnnual Reports\nBBAU Newsletter\nJournals\nIQAC\nSchool & Dept.\nSchool\nAmbedkar School of Social Sciences\nLife Sciences\nInformation Science & Technology\nEarth & Environmental Sciences\nEducation\nHome Science\nLegal Studies\nManagement and Commerce\nPhysical & Decision Sciences\nLanguages and Literature\nMedia and Communication\nAgricultural Sciences & Technology\nPharmaceutical Sciences\nSanskrit & Indic Studies\nSchool of Vocational & Futuristic Studies\nSchool of Yoga Naturopathy & Cognitive Studies\nSchool of Performing Arts\nSchool of Engineering & Technology\nCentre\'s & Institute\nSatellite Centre, Amethi\nUniversity Institute of Engineering & Technology\nOther / Important Centre\'s\nProgramme\nDoctoral\nPh.D\nM.Phil\nIntegrated Courses\nB.Sc.-M.Sc\nBBA-LLB\nPost Graduate\nM.Sc..\nM.Tech..\nM.A...\nLLM\nM.Pharm\nUnder Graduate\nB.Tech.\nBBA\nB.Sc.\nOthers\nDiploma\nCertificate\nResearch\nDirector Research & Development\nResearch & Development\nPh.D Awarded\nOngoing Ph.D Research\nM.Phil / Ph.D Regulations\nAwards and Honors\nProjects\nCompleted & On-going\nGuidelines for Research Project\nCommittee\nInstitutional Ethics Committee\nInstitutional Biosafety Committee\nPublication\nLast 5 Years\nCitations\nPatents\nUn