ings of the courses and teaching plans, admission related matters and all other academic issues in consultation with all Deans, Heads, Faculty and Central administration of the University.\nAt present the activities related to Research innovations and academic development in tune of local, national and global aspects are also co-ordinated by this office. The Dean Academic Affairs is co-ordinating Centre of Industry Institution Partnership Programs to facilitate Industrial collaborations and training and MoUs with various Research Institutes, universities and Centre of Excellence in India and Abroad.'),(313,'Alumni','See content','Not Available','drmodilko@gmail.com','https://www.bbau.ac.in/Alumni.aspx','Alumni\nFaculty\nSocial Initiative\nCareer\ne-Learning\nAccreditation\nAchievements\nLibrary\nCampus Ambience\nBBAU ERP: Samarth\n????? ???????\nSitemap\nBabasaheb Bhimrao Ambedkar University, Lucknow\n????????? ?????? ???????? ?????????????\nBabasaheb Bhimrao Ambedkar University\n( A Central University )\nAccredited \'A++\' Grade by NAAC (2023)\nNIRF Ranked 37\nISO 14001:2015\nAbout\nAbout\nUniversity\nVision & Mission\nAct & Statutes\nAcademic Ordinance\nPublic Self Disclosure\nKulgeet\nContact\nUniversity Gallery\'s\nEvent Gallery\nPress/Media Gallery\nVideo Gallery\nAdministration\nStatutory Bodies\nBoard of Management\nAcademic Council\nPlanning Board\nFinance Committee\nAdministration\nVisitor\nChancellor\nVice Chancellor\nOmbudsman\nRegistrar\nFinance Officer\nController Of Examination\nProctor\nDean Student Welfare\nResearch & Development\nDirector IQAC\nHindi Cell\nLibrarian\nDean Academic affairs\nAlumni Cell\nChief Vigilance Officer\nDeans of School\nHeads of Department\nOther / Important Centre\'s\nAcademics\nAcademics\nDean Academic Affairs\nM.Phil / Ph.D Regulations\nMOU\nConsultancy\nCourse folder\nAcademic Calender\nHolidays\nInstitutional Academic Integrity Panel (IAIP)\nCentre for Industry Institution Partnership Program (CIIPP)\nIQAC\nAbout\nIQAC\n